---
title: Sizzling Beef Stir-Fry over Jasmine Rice
description: Stir-fries are a handy dish for weeknights because you can get them on the table quickly with minimal fuss. Just prep your protein and veg, whip together a simple sauce, and let those ingredients sizzle in the pan. For this version, we’re tossing beef cubes, bell pepper, and bok choy in a marinade of ginger, garlic, and soy sauce. It’s simple yet tremendously satisfying.
